cross: Rhyncattleanthe Village Chief Beauty x Rhyncholaeliocattleya Shinfong Vivid
location: National Cheng Kung University Fall Orchid Show, Taiwan

measurements.description: Two large, intensely colored wide, open, flat and fragrant flowers on one 12-cm inflorescence; sepals broadly lineate, saturated plum-purple; petals overlapping, rhomboid, heavily ruffled margins, plum-purple; lip open, showing column, flaring dark velvet purple, subtle orange eyes, beautifully crisped at margin; column purple; substance firm; texture velvety.
